## Change log

### 3.0.1 - 2010-03-05

* Removed dead code.
* Added change log file to the project.

### 3.0.0 - 2010-02-15

* Major overhaul of the namespace structure.
* Use of .Net framework 4.0, instead of 2.0.
* Removed a few less decent classes.
* Removed several utility functions, and added some to get assembly information.
* Moved out cryptographic classes and modules (they are now part of the applications needing them).
* Updated the ProgressbarWithPercentage class to the latest available version.
* Minor improvements all over the codebase.
* Made the project publicly available under the GPL on SourceForge.

### 2.0.3 - 2009-05-21

* Added BugSubmitter: A dialogue that enables user to submit various types of bugs with build in validation. Sends it's info to a webservice.
* Added PasswordDialog: Password editing dialogue with optional authentication and live validation .
* Added SimpleLoginDialog: A simple login dialogue that prompts for a password.
* Added FileDownloader: A class for downloading files in the background that supports info about their progress, the total progress, cancellation, pausing, and resuming. The downloads will run on a separate thread so you don't have to worry about multihreading yourself.
* Refactored CryptoProvider: Now allows you to pass more advanced settings for AES and offers easier to use methods for RSA, DES and TrippleDES.
* Refactored CryptoStr: Has been rewritten to work with the new CryptoProvider and is now easier to use.
* Refactored Updater: A bug in the version compare algorithm has been fixed.
* Refactored BruteForceAttacker: New version included.
* Various bug fixes and other improvements.

### 2.0.2 - 2009-02-26

* A variety of bug fixed and new features, including an alpha of BruteForceHashAttacker.

### 2.0.1 - 2008-11-30

* Revised the assembly structure (The FW is now a lot more modular, and there is no need to include everything in your application).
* Added Classes.Cryptography namespace in Bn.Core assembly with powerful CryptoStr and CyrptoProvider classes.
* Revised MathConverter class.
* Small bug fixes in Time and Clock classes.

### 2.0.0 - 2008-10-29

* Tons of new functionality.
* Refactoring: Improved naming conventions.
* Refactoring: Increased efficiency of several algorithms.

### 1.2.0 - 2008-09-19

