* Added Control ControlPanel to the FW.
* Fixed some bugs concerning the accessors in the declarations of events in a few of the older classes.

### 1.1.0 - 2008-09-16

* Upgraded several classes, including DynStr and MathConverter.
* Added classes Time and Clock.
* Included the XML documentation file.

